isn't easy these days.

627
00:34:01,117 --> 00:34:02,236
You gotta be kidding me.

628
00:34:02,517 --> 00:34:04,037
You're such a nice pretty girl.

629
00:34:04,156 --> 00:34:05,357
You must be very popular.

630
00:34:06,597 --> 00:34:07,496
Thank you.

631
