637
00:34:32,637 --> 00:34:34,317
Hello? Excuse me.

638
00:34:34,344 --> 00:34:35,556
We're stuck in the elevator.

639
00:34:35,556 --> 00:34:36,396
I think it's broken.

640
00:34:36,396 --> 00:34:37,677
Can you send someone to fix it?

641
00:34:37,677 --> 00:34:39,556
I see it. We're sending someone over.

642
00:34:39,556 --> 00:34:40,757
Okay. Thanks. Please hurry!

643
00:34:40,757 --> 00:34:41,357
Right away.

644
00:34:42,357 --> 00:34:43,837
Just a moment. They're working on it.

645
00:34:47,996 --> 00:34:49,036
Could you come

646
00:34:49,036 --> 00:34:51,157
and give a lecture to our managers?

647
00:34:51,916 --> 00:34:53,357
That would be wonderful.

648
00:34:54,357 --> 00:34:55,116
Yes.

649
00:34:55,837 --> 00:34:56,637
Thank you.

650
00:34:56,637 --> 00:34:58,516
The subscriber you dialed is busy.

651
00:34:58,797 --> 00:35:00,036
Why isn't he answering?

652
00:35:06,837 --> 00:35:09,476
Mr. Li, Barry and I
are stuck in the elevator.

653
00:35:09,797 --> 00:35:10,728
The elevator's broken.

654
00:35:11,596 --> 00:35:12,677
Barry isn't doing well.

655
00:35:12,916 --> 00:35:13,717
Do something quick.

656
00:35:23,916 --> 00:35:25,197
Don't be scared. It'll be okay.

657
00:35:26,197 --> 00:35:26,877
Light's back on!

658
00:35:28,596 --> 00:35:29,288
Light's back on.

659
00:35:31,837 --> 00:35:32,677
It's going up.

660
00:35:33,757 --> 00:35:34,396
Barry.

661
00:35:34,396 --> 00:35:35,116
Barry.

662
00:35:35,116 --> 00:35:36,277
I'm so terribly sorry.

663
00:35:36,277 --> 00:35:37,116
Are you okay?

664
00:35:37,237 --> 00:35:38,036
Are you alright?

665
00:35:39,516 --> 00:35:40,396
Restroom.

666
00:35:41,277 --> 00:35:41,797
I'll help.

667
00:35:41,797 --> 00:35:42,797
Let's go to the restroom.

668
00:35:46,076 --> 00:35:46,677
Any tissues?

669
00:35:48,956 --> 00:35:49,877
Got any tissues?

670
00:35:50,757 --> 00:35:51,916
Yes.

671
00:35:59,757 --> 00:36:01,277
Didn't expect such a nice club

672
00:36:02,396 --> 00:36:03,596
