674
00:36:09,277 --> 00:36:10,157
Sign here, right?

675
00:36:10,157 --> 00:36:11,757
(One Hour Ago)

676
00:36:11,757 --> 00:36:12,717
Is everything arranged?

677
00:36:13,317 --> 00:36:14,717
All arranged. Don't worry.

678
00:36:15,956 --> 00:36:16,680
Thanks.

679
00:36:16,956 --> 00:36:17,556
No problem.

680
00:36:20,357 --> 00:36:22,237
Come on. Have another drink.

681
00:36:28,916 --> 00:36:29,704
Mr. Li,

682
00:36:31,436 --> 00:36:34,956
