686
00:36:55,076 --> 00:36:56,996
What is it?

687
00:36:57,237 --> 00:36:58,717
Barry, I understand.

688
00:36:59,076 --> 00:37:02,556
GST can't afford another
harassment incident anytime soon.

689
00:37:03,116 --> 00:37:05,197
I've already calmed Hailun down.

690
00:37:05,637 --> 00:37:07,277
